Kindly use this scripts in redhat distributed linux machines.
While installing kubernates make sure that your servers has more than 2 core
Don't forget to copy the join token from master which will be available after kubeadm init command.
I have configured the hostname of each server like master and worker-node1 like this.
I would like to thank the https://www.linuxtechi.com/install-kubernetes-1-7-centos7-rhel7/ for helping.
